717
01:29:29,630 --> 01:29:30,890
Don't go!

718
01:29:33,970 --> 01:29:35,460
Come back.

719
01:29:35,600 --> 01:29:38,130
Yuji!

720
01:29:44,180 --> 01:29:45,899
Marlene.

721
01:29:58,960 --> 01:30:01,989
Yuji, do you know who I am?

722
01:30:02,029 --> 01:30:03,029
It's Marlene.

723
01:30:03,029 --> 01:30:04,859
Yuji, be strong!

724
01:30:05,600 --> 01:30:06,859
Yuji.

725
01:30:35,560 --> 01:30:38,289
