726
01:30:40,170 --> 01:30:43,189
Yuji, answer me.

727
01:30:44,869 --> 01:30:46,310
Answer me.

728
01:31:05,989 --> 01:31:11,430
The Prophecy Syndromes that stimulates the fighting nature has turned against us.

729
01:31:11,770 --> 01:31:15,130
Did it make the pilot break down?

730
01:31:16,439 --> 01:31:22,899
We're like orphans abandoned by their mother.

731
01:32:24,640 --> 01:32:25,939
Blue bugs.

732
01:32:39,250 --> 01:32:40,590
I ...

733
